      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m looking to find a new home for my trusty car, and she\u2019s a real gem! It\u2019s been so well-taken care of and still runs like a dream\u2014perfect for weekend getaways or just zipping around town. It\u2019s in great shape and ready to hit the road with its next owner. If you\u2019re looking for a reliable ride that\u2019s been loved, this is the one for you. Come say hi and take it for a spin!",
